<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Taylor Made Social AI</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts import for Poppins and Open Sans -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Poppins:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --emerald: #2E7D32;
            --charcoal: #2C2C2C;
            --off-white: #F7F7F7;
            --gold: #D4AF37;
            --sage: #9CAF88;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--off-white);
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--emerald);
        }

        .hero {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .subheading {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--emerald);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.2);
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--charcoal);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .about-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">✨ Taylor Made Social AI</div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Helping Local Businesses Grow with AI-Powered Social Media</h1>
        <p class="subheading">Save time while consistently showing up online with custom content designed specifically for your business.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Book Your Free Strategy Call</a>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Hi! I’m Taylor.</h2>
            <p>I help local businesses grow through strategic AI-assisted social media management.</p>
            <p><strong>My goal is simple:</strong> Create beautiful content that attracts customers while giving business owners more time to focus on running their business.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
